high_descs: Turn around and walk to a diningtable in front, to its nearer long side.
Pick up a bread from the diningtable.
Go back where you came from, notice a fridge right next to you on your right, so step forward, so walk around the corner and face the fridge.
Place the bread inside the fridge.
Go back to the diningtable.
Pick up a butterknife from the diningtable.
Return to the fridge.
Cut the bread in the fridge with the butterknife.
anns.task_desc: Using the butterknife, cut the bread in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table behind you; face the side of the table where handles of cookware pointing to you.
Pick up a loaf of bread on the table.
Turn left and then turn left at refrigerator; face the refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, put the loaf of bread on the bottom of refrigerator; close refrigerator when done.
Turn left and then turn right; walk toward the table in front left; walk around the table to the left side of it; face it.
Pick up a utensil knife on the right side of the table.
Turn right and walk around the table and walk toward the refrigerator on your front left; turn left and face the refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, slice the loaf of bread; close refrigerator when done.
anns.task_desc: Put a loaf of bread in refrigerator and slice it with a knife there.
